RHR-Lin-CP-AL solver

Copyright 2026 Benqi Liu.

This directory contains Benqi Liu's source snapshot used for the
RHR-Lin-CP-AL row in "Restarted Reflected Halpern Acceleration for Augmented
Primal--Dual Methods." Its non-augmented branch supplies the corresponding
linearized control. The research additions include the linearized augmented
primal--dual update, reflected Halpern iteration, experiment profiles, and
release documentation.

Low-level GPU QP infrastructure and input utilities are adapted from
Apache-2.0 licensed first-order optimization software. Original copyright and
license notices are retained in the source files and LICENSE. Related solvers
and papers are cited for attribution and comparison; this release is not
affiliated with or endorsed by their authors or institutions.
